@startuml
title Enterprise AI-Buildable Specification Process Flow

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam activity {
  BorderColor #444444
  BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
  DiamondBackgroundColor #FFF8E1
  DiamondBorderColor #B26A00
  StartColor #2E7D32
  EndColor #2E7D32
  BarColor #666666
  ArrowColor #444444
}

start

:Define System Constitution;
note right
Purpose
Boundaries
Invariants
Governance model
Lifecycle model
end note

:Define Requirements;
note right
Functional
Non-functional
Security
Identity
Data governance
Operations
end note

:Define Architecture (C4);
note right
System Context
Containers
Components
Deployment
end note

:Define UX Information Architecture;
note right
Canonical object model
Navigation
Queues
Drill-down rules
end note

:Define UX Style Guide;
note right
Vocabulary
Interaction rules
State visibility
Anti-patterns
end note

:Define Design System;
note right
Tokens
Layout
Components
States
Accessibility
end note

:Define Domain Model;
note right
Entities
Fields
Enums
Relationships
Lifecycle states
end note

:Define Screen Contracts;
note right
Routes
Purpose
Data dependencies
Actions
UI states
end note

:Define Component Contracts;
note right
Props
Behavior
Allowed usage
Forbidden usage
end note

:Define Decision Tables;
note right
Review rules
Approval thresholds
Routing
Promotion logic
end note

:Define Integration Contracts;
note right
External systems
Inputs / outputs
Auth
Retries
Ownership of truth
end note

:Create Execution Specification Pack;
note right
API contracts
Event model
State transitions
Permissions
Concurrency
Repo structure
end note

:Define Acceptance & Test Harness;
note right
Golden paths
Edge cases
Integration tests
Performance tests
end note

if (Specification complete and sufficiently unambiguous?) then (yes)
  :AI Coding Agent Implementation;
  :Validation Loop;
  if (Failures, ambiguity, or drift found?) then (yes)
    :Return to relevant specification stage;
    -->[refine] :Define Requirements;
  else (no)
    :Production-Ready System;
    stop
  endif
else (no)
  :Refine missing artifacts;
  --> :Define Requirements;
endif

@enduml